---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sim8085 - Privacy Policy" showActions={false}  fullwidth={false} fullHeight={false} smallFooter={false}>
  <section class="privacy-policy max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8 px-6">
    <header class="mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold  mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class=""><strong>Effective Date:</strong> October, 2024</p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold  mb-2">Introduction</h2>
      <p class="">
        Welcome to <strong>Sim8085</strong>! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our website at
        <a href="https://www.sim8085.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline dark:text-blue-400">https://www.sim8085.com</a> and our services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Data Collection</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">We may collect the following user data to provide and improve our services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><strong>Name</strong>: If provided, we collect your name to personalize your user experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Email</strong>: If applicable, we collect your email address to provide services such as account creation, notifications, and important service updates.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">
        If you choose to sign up using a third-party service (e.g., Google Login), we will capture your name, email address, and profile picture from that service.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Non-Personal Data Collection</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We use <strong>PostHog</strong> for analytics purposes to help us understand how you interact with our website and improve the user experience. We may also use cookies to collect non-personal data, which may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><strong>Device information</strong> (e.g., browser type, operating system)</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> (e.g., pages visited, actions taken)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We do not share your personal data with third parties except as required for legal compliance or to provide services through third-party service providers (e.g., analytics). Your privacy is important to us, and we ensure that your information remains confidential.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Updates to Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We may update this Privacy Policy as needed to reflect changes in our services or to comply with legal requirements. Users will be informed of significant updates via email or through the website. Continued use of our services after receiving notice of these changes indicates your acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Contact Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@sim8085.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline dark:text-blue-400">support@sim8085.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        The services provided by <strong>sim8085</strong> are intended for educational purposes and should not be used as a substitute for professional or expert advice. We strive for accuracy but do not guarantee that the simulation outputs or the information provided are completely error-free.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>
